summary: Book of Boy’s Club - $BOBC is based on the works of Matt ​Furie, known for his iconic comic ​character Pepe the Frog. By investing ​in BOBO, you are buying into a piece of ​modern internet folklore that has ​broad cultural recognition and ​impact. The value of BOBO could ​appreciate as the art and stories of ​Matt Furie gain historical significance ​and continue influencing various media ​forms.
